        </h1>
        <p class="lead mb-4" style="color: #A0A0B8; font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7;">
          CoupleLens combines AI-powered relationship assistance with professional therapist services to help couples thrive at every stage of their journey.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
